<html>
<head>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
	<script src="js/jquery-1.11.0.js"></script>
	<script src="js/storyboards.js"></script>
	<script src="js/bootstrap.js"></script>

	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Language Learners</title>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-xs-6 storytitle">
				<h1>
     				 Storyboards
				</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-6">
				<select class="interests" id="interests" onchange="changeInterest()">
					<option value="News">News</option>
					<option value="Food">Food</option>
					<option value="Sports">Sports</option>
					<option value="Exercise">Exercise</option>
				</select>
			</div>
		</div>			
		<div class="row">
    		<div class="container storystyle"> 
    			<p> This is where the text will go. The text is basically a story that relates to that topic of interest chosen above. </p>
    		</div>
		</div>

    	<div class="row">
    		<div class="col-xs-4 text-center">
				<a type="button" class="btn btn-link btn-lg back-btn" href="/">
					<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
					<span>Back</span>
				</a>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-4 text-center">
				<a type="button" class="btn btn-link btn-lg next-btn" href="#">
					<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-book"></span>
					<span>Next Story</span>
				</a>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-4 text-center">
				<a type="button" class="btn btn-link btn-lg word-btn" href="#">
					<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-list-alt"></span>
					<span>Word List</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</body>
</html>
